data.description: SCREAMING DEAL on this charmer with opportunity for days! With just a bit of elbow grease, this home will seriously shine! Hard to find one-level living on a large lot. Hardwood floors with wood burning fireplace and ductless heating/cooling in the living room. Beautifully landscaped and fenced front yard with cozy, comfortable porch. Large backyard that is also fully fenced and a side yard with built-in catio. Quiet location in Clackamas county, so lower property taxes and North Clackamas schools.  Great chance for a first time buyer, down-sizer, or a someone looking for a fantastic investment property. **DON'T LET INTEREST RATES KEEP YOU FROM MAKING A MOVE -- RATE BUY DOWN OPPORTUNITY WITH THE RIGHT OFFER**
